Epidemiology
Source of the outbreak(s) or origin of infection: vectors
Epidemiological comments: coordinates modified to protect confidentiality as required by South African Legislation.

Control measures
Measures applied: vaccination permitted (if a vaccine exists), no treatment of affected animals.
Measures to be applied: vaccination in response to the outbreak(s), screening, quarantine

